OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTUC: Government failing to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprotect workers from AI    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The TUC is calling for stronger rules  
OL,6, to protect workers from decisions made 
OL,7, by artificial intelligence systems.    
OL,9,FAI-powered technologies are now making 
OL,10,F"high-risk, life changing" decisions   
OL,11,Fabout workers' lives including         
OL,12,Fline-managing, hiring and firing       
OL,13,Fstaff", said the body which represents 
OL,14,Funions.                                
OL,16,FBut a new law will "dilute" existing   
OL,17,Fprotections, it said.                  
OL,19,FThe government said the TUC's          
OL,20,Fassessment was "wrong" and has said    
OL,21,Fsafeguards will remain in place.       
